cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text classification. It could also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it deals with social media data. Additionally, it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a deep learning model for fake news detection. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with the classification of information and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as fake news can be considered a security threat.
